snippet.title: HawkZombie Plays: Rainbow City (Demo)
snippet.description:
This is, quite possibly, the cutest G-darn game I've played in FOR-EV-URRRRR. Kato really did a number on this one. So much so, that I had to test myself for the diabeetus after playing.

About halfway through we see why I made a !save bot for my channel.

https://kato-san.itch.io/rainbowcity

Originally broadcast on http://twitch.tv/hawkzombie 

Goofy, irreverent commentary & voices during game play, moderate swearing, and adult innuendo/references.

Intro/Outro background originally done by https://www.facebook.com/tomgillingham2d3danimator

Intro/Outro Music - "Miami Nights - Extended Theme" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
